ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectOrder Acknowledging Receipt of the Assessments Done Pursuant to Subsection 23(1) of the Act
PrecisOrder acknowledging the receipt by Her Excellency the Governor General in Council of the assessments done and the potential addition of 17 wildlife species to schedule 1 pursuant to subsections 23(1) and 27(1.1) of the SPECIES AT RISK ACT, of the Committee on the Status of Endangered Wildlife in Canada (COSEWIC).
